Introduction

Fatou is a Senegalese singer and model who works under DR Music. She is the leader of the multinational girl group BLACKSWAN.

She used to be a model under Cineline Entertainment before being scouted by DR and becoming a trainee. She was introduced as the fourth member of BLACKSWAN on July 8, 2020.
